IN RE PRISCILLA A. S241995 Supreme Court of California OCTOBER 11, 2017 Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Chin, Corrigan, Liu, Cuéllar and Kruger, JJ.

The above-captioned matter is transferred to the Court of Appeal, Second Appellate District, Division One, with directions to vacate its decision and to reconsider the cause in light of In re R.T. (2017) 3 Cal.5th 622, 220 Cal.Rptr.3d 770, 399 P.3d 1. ( Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.528(d).)
